"still have the knowledge and skill to master their mounts whilst in full "
"panoply. Talented squires are sometimes given command of small units in "
"Wesnoth’s army, where they gain experience with fellow troops and honing "
"their prowess in battle.\n"
"\n"
"<span color='#c7c7c7'><i>If you’re a veteran player, you’ll notice that "
"Deoran is based off the Cavalryman, but lacks the Cavalryman’s blade and "
"impact resistances. This was done to simplify the unit, so as not to "
"overwhelm new players.</i></span>"
msgstr ""
